params.sqlcmd: "select " +" T_ODR_CTL.\\"ODR_CTL_NO\\" as \\"ODR_CTL_NO\\" " +"from " +" T_ODR_CTL " +"where " +" T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ODR_CTL.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ODR_CTL.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = '0'"

"select " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_ANAME\\" as \\"CUST_ANAME\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"OWN_ORG_CD\\" as \\"OWN_ORG_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\" as \\"OWN_PERSON_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"PARTIAL_SHIP_INST_FLG\\" as \\"PARTIAL_SHIP_INST_FLG\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"EXCH_TYP\\" as \\"EXCH_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\" as \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_CD\\" as \\"TAX_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\" as \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_EFF_PRIOD\\" as \\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_EFF_PRIOD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_EFF_TERM_FLG\\" as \\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_EFF_TERM_FLG\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"DETAIL_ROUND_TYP\\" as \\"ROUND_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_CUST " +"where " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DLV_LOC_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_LT\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"CAL_NO\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DLV_LOC_NAME\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DEPO_WH_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"SHIP_WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_CUST_BASE, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_CUST_BASE.SHIP_WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST_BASE.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST_BASE.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"DEPO_TYP\\" as \\"DEPO_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"TAX_CD\\" as \\"TAX_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_SPEC " +"where " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST\\" as \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" " +"from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD') " +"order by " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" desc"

"select " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_NAME\\" as \\"USER_NAME\\", " +" USER_MST.\\"SECTION_CD\\" as \\"SECTION_CD\\", " +" NULL as \\"ORG_CD\\", " +" NULL as \\"ORG_NAME\\", " +" NULL as \\"ORG_ANAME\\" " +"from " +" USER_MST " +"where " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_INFO_COM_IF_CTRL_NO\\" as \\"ODR_INFO_COM_IF_CTRL_NO\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_SEQ\\" as \\"ODR_SEQ\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_TYP\\" as \\"ODR_TYP\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"IF_TYP\\" as \\"IF_TYP\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"INFO_TYP_CD\\" as \\"INFO_TYP_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CUST_ODR_NO\\" as \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\", " +" \\"DLV_LOC_CD_EIAJ\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"DLV_LOC_NAME_KANJI\\" as \\"DLV_LOC_NAME_KANJI\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CUS_DLV_CD\\" as \\"CUS_DLV_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CUS_DLV_KEY_CD\\" as \\"CUS_DLV_KEY_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"FREE_REMARK\\" as \\"FREE_REMARK\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"REMARK\\" as \\"REMARK\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CLIENT_BARCODE_INF\\" as \\"CLIENT_BARCODE_INF\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CLIENT_REMARK\\" as \\"CLIENT_REMARK\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CLIENT_REMARK_KANJI\\" as \\"CLIENT_REMARK_KANJI\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"SLIP_PRICE_PRINT_TYP\\" as \\"SLIP_PRICE_PRINT_TYP\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"OLD_ITEM_ODR_ACPT_F\\" as \\"OLD_ITEM_ODR_ACPT_F\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"FORCED_ERR_ITEM_ODR_ACPT_F\\" as \\"FORCED_ERR_ITEM_ODR_ACPT_F\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"BUYER_NAME\\" as \\"BUYER_NAME\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"PUCH_ODR_QTY_TOTAL\\" as \\"PUCH_ODR_QTY_TOTAL\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"UNIT_CD_ORG\\" as \\"UNIT_CD_ORG\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"BUYER_ORG_CD\\" as \\"BUYER_ORG_CD\\" " +"from " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF " +"where " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"SYSTEM_PROC_TYP\\" = '0' " +" and T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = '0' " +" and T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"PROC_TYP\\" = '1' " +"order by " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_ACPT_DATE\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CUST_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_ACPT_PROC_ODR\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_INFO_COM_IF_CTRL_NO\\", " +" T_ODR_INFO_COM_IF.\\"ODR_SEQ\\""

"select " +" SYS_BUSINESS_MESSAGE.\\"MSG_CD\\" as \\"MSG_CD\\", " +" SYS_BUSINESS_MESSAGE.\\"MSG\\" as \\"MSG\\" " +"from " +" SYS_BUSINESS_MESSAGE " +"where " +" SYS_BUSINESS_MESSAGE.\\"MSG_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DLV_LOC_CD\\" as \\"DLV_LOC_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_LT\\" as \\"TRANSPORT_LT\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_CD\\" as \\"TRANSPORT_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DLV_LOC_NAME\\" as \\"DLV_LOC_NAME\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"CAL_NO\\" as \\"CAL_NO\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_TYP\\" as \\"TRANSPORT_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DEPO_WH_CD\\" as \\"DEPO_WH_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"SHIP_WH_CD\\" as \\"SHIP_WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_CUST_BASE, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_CUST_BASE.SHIP_WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_CUST_BASE.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST_BASE.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST_BASE.\\"DLV_LOC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_ODR.\\"ODR_NO\\" as \\"ODR_NO\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"REMAIN_UNCONFIRM_ODR_QTY\\" as \\"REMAIN_UNCONFIRM_ODR_QTY\\", " +" T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_CD\\" as \\"CUST_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_CTL.\\"ODR_CTL_NO\\" as \\"ODR_CTL_NO\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ODR.\\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"CURRNCY_CD\\" as \\"CURRNCY_CD\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"ODR_UNIT_PRICE\\" as \\"ODR_UNIT_PRICE\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"ODR_TYP\\" as \\"ODR_TYP\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_BALANCE\\" as \\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_BALANCE\\" " +"from " +" T_ODR, " +" T_ODR_CTL " +"where " +" T_ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = T_ODR_CTL.ODR_CTL_NO " +" and T_ODR.\\"ODR_TYP\\" = '2' " +" and T_ODR.\\"REMAIN_UNCONFIRM_ODR_QTY\\" > 0 " +" and T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ODR.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = '0' " +"order by " +" T_ODR.\\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"ODR_NO\\", " +" T_ODR.\\"REMAIN_UNCONFIRM_ODR_QTY\\" " +" "
"select " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CODE\\" as \\"CODE\\" " +"from " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE " +"where " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"SYS_CLASS\\" = 'SALES' " +" and SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CLASS_CODE\\" = ?"
